@startuml order-state-machine
title LeSonStore — Order status state machine (Bước 4)

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
  BorderColor #333
}

[*] --> AWAITING_PAYMENT : create (VNPAY)\n/create (COD → processing*)

note right of AWAITING_PAYMENT
  * COD create có thể set processing
  trực tiếp tại create — không qua FSM
end note

AWAITING_PAYMENT --> processing : vnpay_return\napplyTransition
AWAITING_PAYMENT --> cancelled : customer_cancel

processing --> shipping : admin_ship\nadmin PUT
processing --> cancelled : customer_cancel

shipping --> delivered : admin_deliver\nadmin PUT

delivered --> [*]
cancelled --> [*]

FAILED --> AWAITING_PAYMENT : retry flow\n(if used)

state "orderStateMachine.js" as FSM {
  state assertTransition
  state applyTransition
}

note bottom of FSM
  emitStatusChanged → order.status.changed
  (sau commit, không trong transaction)
end note

@enduml
